            "margin_top": 0,
            "margin_bottom": 16
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "text_content": "<p>Introducing the <strong>Elaren</strong> whitening routine: purple mouthwash for instant brightness, enamel-safe strips for deeper results, and a hands-free LED device to speed things up.</p><p>It is built around three simple products that each do one job well, and work even better together. All of them are gentle on your enamel.</p><p>Here is what each part does:</p>",
            "text_font_size": 16,
            "text_color": "#000000",
            "text_alignment": "left",
            "line_height": 1.6,
            "highlight_words": "Elaren,enamel-safe,hands-free",
