            "symptom_title": "Hands-free LED Device",
            "symptom_description": "<p>The U-shaped device whitens every tooth at once and stays in place hands-free, so you can get on with your day while it works.</p>",
            "symptom_science_text": "<p>Rechargeable and reusable, the durable hero of your routine.</p>",
