        {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "text_content": "<p>Ordinary strips can whiten, but they slip around and many people find they sting. Elaren strips are enamel-safe and close-fit, so most people can whiten comfortably.</p><p><strong>How does it work?</strong></p><p>Start your day with a purple mouthwash rinse for instant brightness. A few times a week, wear the enamel-safe strips for about 30 minutes for deeper whitening. When you want to speed things up, pop in the hands-free LED device while you get ready.</p><p>Most people notice a cleaner, fresher feel from the first rinse, and visible results from the strips after the first use. Individual results vary, so take a photo on day one and compare as you go.</p>",
            "text_font_size": 16,
            "text_color": "#000000",
