        {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "text_content": "<p>This is the best part, it is genuinely simple.</p><p><strong>Step 1: Rinse.</strong> Swish the purple mouthwash for about 30 seconds for instant brightness.</p><p><strong>Step 2: Strip.</strong> A few times a week, wear the enamel-safe strips for about 30 minutes.</p><p><strong>Step 3: Accelerate.</strong> Pop in the hands-free LED device while you get ready, then get on with your day.</p><p>That is it. A daily rinse, strips a few times a week, and the LED device whenever you want to speed things up. Take a photo on day one and watch your smile brighten.</p>",
