        },
        {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "text_content": "<p><strong>Chloe R., verified purchase:</strong> I honestly did not expect much, but three weeks in my smile is noticeably brighter and there was no sting. The strips stay put and the mouthwash is my favourite part.</p>",
            "text_font_size": 15,
            "text_color": "#000000",
            "text_alignment": "left",
            "line_height": 1.5,
            "margin_top": 0,
            "margin_bottom": 20
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "divider_line",
          "settings": {
            "divider_width": 60,
            "divider_height": 1,
            "divider_color": "#e0e0e0",
            "divider_alignment": "center",
            "margin_top": 16,
            "margin_bottom": 16
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "text_content": "<p><strong>Daniel W.:</strong> Easy to keep up with and gentle on my teeth. Day 7 and I can already see a difference.</p><p><strong>Aisha B.:</strong> The hands-free device is my favourite, I use it while I get ready. Fresh breath and a brighter smile.</p><p><strong>Ryan C.:</strong> Two weeks in and friends have noticed. No sensitivity at all.</p>",
            "text_font_size": 15,
            "text_color": "#000000",
            "text_alignment": "left",
            "line_height": 1.5,
            "margin_top": 0,
            "margin_bottom": 28
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "divider_line",
          "settings": {
            "divider_width": 80,
            "divider_height": 1,
            "divider_color": "#e0e0e0",
            "divider_alignment": "center",
            "margin_top": 30,
            "margin_bottom": 30
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "article_heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading_text": "<p>My own 30-day test</p>",
            "heading_font_size": 28,
            "text_alignment": "left",
            "margin_top": 0,
            "margin_bottom": 16
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "text_content": "<p>When my kit arrived, I did the simple thing: I photographed my teeth on day one, in the same bathroom light. Not the most flattering photo, but that was the point, I wanted an honest starting line.</p><p>The first few days, my smile looked brighter from the mouthwash alone. By the end of the first week, the strips had done visible work. No sensitivity, no sting, I just rinsed each morning and wore the strips a few times a week.</p><p>Around day 14, a friend asked if I'd had my teeth done. That was the moment it felt real.</p><p>By day 30 I put the two photos side by side. The difference was clear to me, though everyone's teeth start in a different place, so individual results vary. What I liked most was how little I had to think about it.</p>",
            "text_font_size": 16,
            "text_color": "#000000",
            "text_alignment": "left",
            "line_height": 1.6,
            "highlight_words": "day one,day 30",
            "highlight_background_color": "#f5f5f5",
