        },
        {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "text_content": "<p>In-chair whitening runs $600 or more a visit, and it is not something you do every day.</p><p>The Complete Kit is $49 today for the LED device plus purple mouthwash and whitening strips. After that, your refill of mouthwash and strips is $29 on subscribe and save, and you can skip, pause or cancel any time.</p><p>Because subscribers get the device 40% off, you are really only paying for the refills you use, which prices the device itself at an effective $20.</p>",
